OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy and
OL,6,Fperhaps thundery showers at first this
OL,7,Fevening with some clear spells.
OL,8,FShowers easing overnight with clear
OL,9,Fspells, but low cloud and rain
OL,10,Fspreading into the south around dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks
OL,13,Fof rain spreading north to all parts
OL,14,Fthrough the day. Breezy around western
OL,15,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
