OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy and windy with showers on
OL,7,FFriday and Saturday, showers may be
OL,8,Fheavy at times. A dry day on Sunday
OL,9,Fwith some long spells of sunshine
OL,10,Fdeveloping.
